WEBVTT

00:04:55.829 --> 00:05:00.979
Almost every single random mass shooter

00:05:01.003 --> 00:05:02.849
has something in common.

00:05:04.035 --> 00:05:06.228
Can anybody guess what that is?

00:05:08.468 --> 00:05:10.363
They want notoriety.

00:05:11.273 --> 00:05:13.454
They want to be famous.

00:05:13.478 --> 00:05:15.372
In fact,

00:05:15.396 --> 00:05:20.946
these murderers
are telling us this themselves.

00:05:21.684 --> 00:05:23.993
The Sandy Hook murderer

00:05:24.017 --> 00:05:26.235
kept a spreadsheet

00:05:26.259 --> 00:05:31.085
of previous mass murderers
and their number of kills.